{"content": "I need to multiply 800 \u00d7 335 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 800\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 0 + 0 = 648\u2081\u2080\n- 335\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 5 = 243 + 27 + 5 = 275\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 648 \u00d7 275 = 178,200\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 178200 \u00f7 9 = 19800 r 0\n- 19800 \u00f7 9 = 2200 r 0\n- 2200 \u00f7 9 = 244 r 4\n- 244 \u00f7 9 = 27 r 1\n- 27 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 0\n- 3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: **301400\u2089**\n\n301400", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 326}